author: jchris
msg: Initial checkin of _changes filters. The prime weak-spot for this approach is that it maintains an OS-process per connected filtered _changes consumer. I'm pretty sure we'll be able to work around this without changing the API, but it'll involve a lot of OS-process bookkeeping. Those enhancements should generally improve show & list performance as well. Punting on them for now, first wanted to get _changes filters implemented so people could give feedback.
